工智能是現時需求最大的行業，過去 5 年間，相關人才的需求平均每年增長 74%</span>。報告又指 15 種新興職業排行榜中，人工智能專家更是名列首位。由此反映，人工智能專才非常受歡迎，充滿發展前景。<br />\n<br />\n學系亦積極鼓勵學生到境外交流，在暑假前往內地、台灣、美國或加拿大等地的著名大學，如北京清華大學、美國麻省理工學院、哥倫比亞大學，從事人工智能相關的學術研究，學習科研技巧，同時培養國際視野。中大工程學院更設有高錕教授科研交流生獎學金，資助學生到境外交流。另外，學系也會推薦學生參加由大企業和專業團體舉辦的科技比賽，一展身手。學生過去在國際程式設計比賽（ICPC）、積體電路電腦輔助設計軟體製作競賽（CAD Contest）等國際比賽均取得佳績。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05fc7cde27d8f6439c52572ffc2bce7fe7531303","tid":2121684,"uid":305631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e709208a28dbacca9db56d6745aead8c9588f817","tid":2121684,"uid":118502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98cb5b5cd2200bde59efba1b8eb45108c885743a","tid":2121684,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T13:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xh38xgh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXh38xgh.png&h=470dbcfc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:14:57.000Z","msg":"ASSO 都有神科?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:19:58.000Z","msg":"Asso仔=神<br />\n神讀咩 嗰科就係神科"},{"pid":"b3fee3ed763dd558ad7ce3ed595f77109d9a2379","tid":2121684,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T18:27:01.000Z","msg":"前景幾好"},{"pid":"a5b9a865035ae642cc8e1b2f2212013295cbdb7f","tid":2121684,"uid":29836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T18:32:10.000Z","msg":"又水人讀AI<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b0abb03cef9bac2621d02352ecf946071f4638","tid":2121684,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T18:33:53.000Z","msg":"係香港讀AI<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38111b75e2c5faab0d796b4f7684eeef33640692","tid"